  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\nAfter moving app to QUO components in  \"Back up your seed phrase\" (Profile > Privacy and Security> Back up seed phrase) several issues have appeared.\r\n1) \"Okay, continue\" and \"Okay, got it\" buttons are too big\r\n2) Validation errors are not aligned with field\r\n3) \"Done\" button is not aligned with keyboard (Android only , and it can cause fail of e2e 5419)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nBack up seed phrase flow is the same as in 1.4.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n1) ![photo_2020-07-16 12 55 18 jpeg 2020-07-16 12-55-50](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/87663189-baeceb00-c763-11ea-82e2-6475321ea0d4.png)\r\n2) ![photo_2020-07-16 12 57 06 jpeg 2020-07-16 12-57-19](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/87663307-e7086c00-c763-11ea-9421-b2963ec7a4a3.png)\r\n3) ![photo_2020-07-16 12 57 59 jpeg 2020-07-16 12-58-14](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/87663370-07d0c180-c764-11ea-83fd-3aea041ecce7.png)\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Create new account\r\n- Open Profile > Settings > Privacy and Security > Back up seed phrase\r\n- Complete flow\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly 16/07/2020\r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n",
